---
title: Pork and Lentil Curry with Naan Bread
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Pork and Lentil Curry with Naan Bread in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-and-lentil-curry-b5237503-d4064f90.jpg
